        <Text/>
        <URI>
          <link internal="true" type="WEAK">
            <target><![CDATA[/sites/docu/opencms-documentation/content-in-opencms/defining-the-schema-of-a-content-type/defining-the-contents-behaviour/appearance-in-the-content-editor/dependent-fields/]]></target>
            <uuid>1f03a57a-db28-11ec-8fb9-0242ac11002b</uuid>
          </link>
        </URI>
      </Link>
    </Section>
    <Section>
      <Caption><![CDATA[Mappings and defaults with macros]]></Caption>
      <Text name="Text0">
        <links/>
        <content><![CDATA[<p>Default values can be set via macros and even for optional elements, the default values can be used for mappings. Read the details here.</p>]]></content>
